title: 12/10 Fantasy Football Podcast: Week 14 Recap - Redemption Week
description:
Reacting to Carson Wentz's injury (2:10) and more from around the NFL before we talk about Redemption Week (8:33) for Kareem Hunt, Jordan Howard and Carlos Hyde ... Winners (15:00) including DeMaryius Thomas and Josh Gordon and losers (21:05) including Christian McCaffrey and Mike Evans ... "Does He Matter?" (27:48) with some interesting young WRs, Week 14 leaders at QB (33:35), RB (35:06), WR (37:50) and TE (39:00) and then a recap of every game with our Fantasy takes (41:00) ... Your emails at fantasyfootball@cbsi.com
